{"word":"Jebusites","slug":"jebusites","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>Jebusites</b> One of the tribes of Canaan<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=5&chapter=7&verse=1'>Deu 7:1</a><br/> Land of, given to Abraham and his descendants<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=15&verse=21'>Gen 15:21</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=2&chapter=3&verse=8'>Exo 3:8</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=2&chapter=3&verse=17'>Exo 3:17</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=2&chapter=23&verse=24'>Exo 23:24</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=5&chapter=20&verse=17'>Deu 20:17</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=2&chapter=33&verse=2'>Exo 33:2</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=2&chapter=34&verse=11'>Exo 34:11</a><br/> Conquered by Joshua<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=43&chapter=10'>Joh 10</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=6&chapter=24&verse=11'>Jos 24:11</a><br/> Conquered by David<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=10&chapter=5&verse=9'>2Sa 5:9</a><br/> Jerusalem within the territory of<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=6&chapter=18&verse=28'>Jos 18:28</a><br/> Not exterminated, but intermarry with the Israelites<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=7&chapter=3&verse=6'>Jdg 3:6</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=15&chapter=9&verse=2'>Ezr 9:2</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=15&chapter=10&verse=44'>Ezr 10:44</a><br/> Pay tribute to Solomon<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=11&chapter=9&verse=21'>1Ki 9:21</a>"}]}